      <title>Temenos 宣布对兴登堡索赔进行独立审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/temenos-will-start-independent-examination-of-hindenburg-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Temenos AG 宣布对兴登堡研究公司上周在一份关于这家瑞士银行软件制造商的报告中​​提出的财务违规指控进行独立调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/temenos-will-start-independent-examination-of-hindenburg-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 16:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
